data.title: My Berlin: that tower again
data.meta_description: The ubiquitous landmark, from around the German capital.
data.text:
I like shiny pointy objects, and if it‚Äôs by deliberate effort or accidental circumstance, the Fernsehturm (TV Tower) slides into many of my photos from Berlin. And if people throughout Berlin can see the tower, how do those who live in or commute through different parts of the capital city view the landmark? After multiple visits between 2005 and 2021, I‚Äôve accumulated over 45 lines-of-sight to the TV Tower around Berlin.
